<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="introduction-n">introduction <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ˌɪntrə'dʌkʃn/    美 /ˌɪntrə'dʌkʃn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>引进；采用：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the introduction of a new method into language teaching
语言教学中新方法的引入</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>入门导读；序言：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>an introduction to the advanced course 
高级课程入门</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The book is a complete <strong>introduction to</strong> all the best Indian films. 
本书完整介绍了印度所有最好的电影。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>介绍；引见：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a letter of introduction 
介绍信</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He <strong>made the introductions</strong> at the party. 
他在晚会上对大家做了介绍。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>This development was only possible with the <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (introduce) of electric-powered engines and lifts.  （2017 全国）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. introduction  </p></div>